org.vmmagic.unboxed

Class Extent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vmmagic.unboxed.Extent

  • public final class Extent
extends Object
    Represents a pointer-sized unsigned integer used for describing a length in bytes. Typical uses include "length" or "size" arguments (e.g., for memcpy).
